'''鼯鼠屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Petaurista''}}）又名'''大飛鼠屬'''，為[[嚙齒目|嚙齒目]][[松鼠科|松鼠科]]的一屬，是一類大型[[飛鼠|飛鼠]]。{{r|Jackson2012}}

==分類==
本屬包含以下物種{{r|MSW3|Choudhury2007|Choudhury2009|Choudhury2013}}：
{{common taxon list|italic=yes
|红白鼯鼠|Petaurista alborufus |Milne-Edwards, 1870
|小鼯鼠|Petaurista elegans |Müller, 1840
|白颊鼯鼠|Petaurista leucogenys |Temminck, 1827
|栗褐鼯鼠|Petaurista magnificus |Hodgson, 1836
|梅丘卡鼯鼠|Petaurista mechukaensis |Choudhury, 2007
|祁靈公山鼯鼠|Petaurista mishmiensis |Choudhury, 2009
|不丹鼯鼠|Petaurista nobilis |Gray, 1842
|棕鼯鼠|Petaurista petaurista |Pallas, 1766
|赤鼯鼠|Petaurista philippensis |Elliot, 1839
|桑朗鼯鼠|Petaurista siangensis |Choudhury, 2013
|灰鼯鼠|Petaurista xanthotis |Milne-Edwards, 1872
}}

還有一些傳統上視為[[亞種|亞種]]，但近期研究被認為應當重新歸類的獨立物種{{r|Jackson2012|Li2013}}：
{{common taxon list|italic=yes
|白腹棕鼯鼠|Petaurista albiventer |Gray, 1834
|灰頭鼯鼠|Petaurista caniceps |Gray, 1842
|大赤鼯鼠|Petaurista grandis |Swinhoe, 1863
|海南鼯鼠|Petaurista hainana |G. Allen, 1925
|白面鼯鼠|Petaurista lena |Thomas, 1907
|白斑鼯鼠|Petaurista marica |Thomas, 1912
|欽敦江鼯鼠|Petaurista sybilla |Thomas and Wroughton, 1916
}}

